// ── Reimagine finished-page screenshot (inlined, full page, full resolution) ──
// A full-resolution render of a Stardust-reimagined page, inlined as a base64 JPEG
// data URI so the result preview can SCROLL through the whole finished page in the
// stubbed demo. Inlined (not a bundled asset) for the same reason as
